51:27.339 --> 51:28.840
- Yeah.
- We're gonna head out to the water.

51:28.965 --> 51:30.508
Come on. Come on.

51:30.592 --> 51:31.801
I'm good, thanks.

51:31.885 --> 51:33.511
You sure? All right.
