Hey, El!

52:45.166 --> 52:46.251
El!

52:46.793 --> 52:48.503
Where are you? Let's get in the pool.

52:48.587 --> 52:50.380
Mr. Waller?
- Hey.

52:50.505 --> 52:51.756
Hey, El!

52:51.840 --> 52:53.091
Will you sign this for me?

52:54.342 --> 52:56.553
It took me like an hour
to find it last night.

53:06.813 --> 53:07.939
Yeah, of course.

53:10.191 --> 53:12.193
Thank you so much.
- Yeah.

53:14.613 --> 53:15.614
There you go.

53:15.697 --> 53:17.657
- Now hold on to that.
- I will.

53:17.741 --> 53:19.075
It's gonna be worth something someday.

53:19.159 --> 53:20.619
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

53:21.286 --> 53:23.413
- Hey.
- Yeah?

53:24.539 --> 53:27.792
