54:13.838 --> 54:15.465
- Kay?
- Hmm?

54:18.260 --> 54:19.469
Okay, you know what?

54:22.931 --> 54:24.516
You know, this is your new home,

54:24.599 --> 54:27.561
and I-I didn't want to say anything
that would taint your...

54:27.644 --> 54:28.979
Your feelings about this house.

54:29.062 --> 54:31.231
