54:31.731 --> 54:33.400
Get it, buddy. Yeah.
Ty, use your core.

54:33.483 --> 54:34.818
Let's go!
Use your core, Ty.

54:34.901 --> 54:36.111
There you go. Lean forward a little bit.

54:36.194 --> 54:37.445
- Yeah. That's it.
- Lean forward.

54:37.529 --> 54:39.573
Use your arms. Your arms.
Going down, Mikey.

54:39.656 --> 54:43.785
I swear, I had no idea
that this was the same house

54:43.910 --> 54:45.996
